Comment.val: /* XML information message to empty a depot */
/*XML information to send the asynchronous response after processing the emptyingDepot Instruction*/

This program empties a depotaccount, for now it only works for fund accounts, not market depots.
This program has no return value because it's async.

ExpSyntax.val: FlwMtr('Error : Account '& Trim(Str({0,5},'15'))&' is already empty','FALSE'LOG)
